\c 7
\s Vana vaIsasikari
\p
\v 1 Nekuvanakomana vaIsasikari: Tora, naPuwa, Jashubhi, naShimironi, vana\x + Gen.. 46.13.\x*.
\v 2 Nevanakomana vaTora: Uzi, naRefaya, naJerieri, naJahimai, naIbhisamu, naShemueri, misoro yeimba yemadzibaba avo\x + 6.33.\x*, kwaTora, varume vane simba neumhare pamazera avo; uwandu hwavo pamazuva aDhavhidhi hwaiva zvuru makumi maviri nezviviri nemazana matanhatu\x + 27.1,24. 7.4,5,7,9,11,40. 2 Sam. 24.1,2,9.\x*.
\v 3 Nevanakomana vaUzi: Izirahiya; nevanakomana vaIzirahiya: Mikayeri naObhadhiya, naJoweri, Ishishiya, vashanu; vese vari misoro.
\v 4 Zvino pamwe navo nemadzinza avo zvichienderana neimba yemadzibaba avo, kwaiva nehondo dzakarongwa dzeuto rehondo zvuru makumi matatu nezvitanhatu; nokuti vaiva nevakadzi nevanakomana vazhinji.
\v 5 Nehama dzavo pakati pemhuri dzose dzaIsasikari, varume vane simba veumhare, zvuru makumi masere nezvinomwe, vese vakaverengwa nedzinza.
\s Vana vaBhenjamini naNafutari
\p
\v 6 \add Vanakomana\add* vaBhenjamini: Bhera, naBhekeri, naJedhiyaeri, vatatu\x + 8.1. Gen.. 46.21. Num.. 26.38.\x*.
\v 7 Nevanakomana vaBhera: Ezibhoni, naUzi, naUziyeri, naJerimoti, naIri, vashanu; misoro yeimba yemadzibaba, varume vane simba veumhare, vakaverengwa nemadzinza, zvuru makumi maviri nezviviri nemakumi matatu nevana.
\v 8 Nevanakomana vaBhekeri: Zemira, naJowashi, naEriezeri, naErioenai, naOmiri, naJeremoti, naAbhiya, naAnatoti\x + 6.60.\x*, naAremeti\x + 6.60.\x*. Ava vese vaiva vanakomana vaBhekeri.
\v 9 Vakaverengwa nedzinza nemazera avo, misoro yeimba yemadzibaba avo, varume vane simba veumhare, zvuru makumi maviri nemazana maviri.
\v 10 Nevanakomana vaJedhiyaeri: Bhirihani. Nevanakomana vaBhirihani: Jehushi, naBhenjamini, naEhudhi, naKenahana, naZetani, naTarishishi, naAhishahari.
\v 11 Ava vese vanakomana vaJedhiyaeri, nemisoro yemadzibaba, varume vane simba veumhare, zvuru gumi nezvinomwe nemazana maviri, vangabudira mauto kuhondo.
\v 12 NaShupimi, naHupimi, vanakomana vaIri; Hushimi, vanakomana vaAheri.
\p
\v 13 Vanakomana vaNafutari: Jazieri, naGuni, naJezeri, naSharumi, vanakomana vaBhiriha.
\s Vana vaManase
\p
\v 14 Vanakomana vaManase\x + Num.. 26.29-33.\x*: Ashirieri \add mukadzi wake\add* waakabereka; murongo wake mukadzi muAramu wakabereka Makiri baba vaGiriyadhi\x + Josh. 17.1.\x*.
\v 15 Makiri ndokutora pana Hupimi nepana Shupimi kuva mukadzi, uye zita rehanzvadzi yake raiva Mahaka\x + 7.16.\x*; uye zita rewechipiri raiva Zerofehadhi; uye Zerofehadhi waiva nevakunda\x + Num.. 26.33.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino Mahaka mukadzi waMakiri wakabereka mwanakomana, ndokutumidza zita rake Pereshi; uye zita remunin'ina wake raiva Shereshi; nevanakomana vake vaiva Urami naRekemu\x + Gen.. 38.4,5.\x*.
\v 17 Nevanakomana vaUramu: Bhedhani\x + 1 Sam. 12.11.\x*. Ava vanakomana vaGiriyadhi, mwanakomana waMakiri, mwanakomana waManase.
\v 18 Hanzvadzi yake Hamoreketi ndokubereka Ishodhi, naAbhiyezeri, naMahara.
\v 19 Vanakomana vaShemidha vaiva: Ahiyani, naShekemu, naRiki, naAniyamu\x + Josh. 17.2.\x*.
\s Vana vaEfuremu
\p
\v 20 Zvino vanakomana vaEfuremu: Shutera, naBheredhi mwanakomana wake, naTahati mwanakomana wake, naEradha mwanakomana wake, naTahati mwanakomana wake\x + Num.. 26.35.\x*,
\v 21 naZabhadhi mwanakomana wake, naShutera mwanakomana wake, naEzeri, naEreyadhi. Varume veGati vakaberekerwa panyika iyo ndokuvauraya, nokuti vaburukira kuzotora zvipfuwo zvavo\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*.
\v 22 Efuremu baba vavo ndokuchema mazuva mazhinji; hama dzake ndokuuya kuzomunyaradza.
\v 23 Zvino wakapinda kumukadzi wake, akabata mimba, ndokubereka mwanakomana; iye ndokutumidza zita rake \add kuti\add* Bheriya; nokuti waiva pakaipa muimba yake.
\v 24 Nemukunda wake waiva Sheera, uyo wakavaka Bheti-Horoni rezasi nerekumusoro, neUzeni-Sheera\x + Josh. 10.10.\x*.
\v 25 NaRefa waiva mwanakomana wake, naReshefi, naTera mwanakomana wake, naTahani mwanakomana wake,
\v 26 Rahadhani mwanakomana wake, Amihudhi mwanakomana wake, Erishama mwanakomana wake\x + Num.. 1.10. 7.48.\x*,
\v 27 Noni mwanakomana wake, Joshua mwanakomana wake\x + Num.. 13.16.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Nefuma yavo nenzvimbo dzavo dzekugara dzaiva Bheteri nemisha yaro\x + Josh. 16.2.\x*; nekumabvazuva Naharani, nekumavirira Gezeri nemisha yaro\x + Josh. 16.3.\x*, neShekemu nemisha yaro, kusvika paGaza nemisha yaro.
\v 29 Nekumiganhu yevana vaManase\x + Josh. 17.7. Josh. 17.11.\x*: Bheti-Sheyani nemisha yaro, Taanaki nemisha yaro, Megidho nemisha yaro, Dhori nemisha yaro. Mune iyi maigara vana vaJosefa mwanakomana waIsraeri.
\s Vanakomana vaAsheri
\p
\v 30 Vanakomana vaAsheri: Imina\x + Gen.. 46.17. Num.. 26.44.\x*, naIshivha\x + Gen.. 46.17. Num.. 26.44.\x*, naIshivhi\x + Gen.. 46.17. Num.. 26.44.\x*, naBheriya, naSera hanzvadzi yavo.
\v 31 Nevanakomana vaBheriya: Hebheri, naMarikiyeri, waiva baba vaBhirizayiti.
\v 32 Hebheri ndokubereka Jafureti, naShomeri, naHotamu, naShuwa hanzvadzi yavo.
\v 33 Nevanakomana vaJafureti: Pasaki, naBhimari, naAshivati. Ndivo vanakomana vaJafureti.
\v 34 Nevanakomana vaShemeri: Ahi, naRohiga, naJehubha, naAramu.
\v 35 Nevanakomana vaHeremu munin'ina wake: Zofa, naImina, naShereshi, naAmari.
\v 36 Vanakomana vaZofa: Suwa, naHarineferi, naShuwari, naBheri, naImira,
\v 37 Bhezeri, naHodhi, naShama, naShirisha, naItirani\x + 7.38.\x*, naBhehera.
\v 38 Nevanakomana vaJeteri\x + 7.38.\x*: Jefune, naPisipa, naAra.
\v 39 Nevanakomana vaUra: Ara, naHanieri, naRizia.
\v 40 Ava vese vana vaAsheri, misoro yeimba yemadzibaba, vakasarudzwa, vane simba veumhare, misoro yemachinda. Uye vakaverengwa nedzinza pamauto pahondo; uwandu hwavo hwaiva varume zvuru makumi maviri nezvitanhatu\x + 9.22.\x*.